      "value": "<p><strong>Speed</strong>&nbsp;25 ft.</p>\n<p><strong>Strength&nbsp;</strong> 16 (+3);&nbsp;<strong>Damage&nbsp;</strong> 1d10 P;&nbsp;<strong>Size&nbsp;</strong> Large (5-ft. reach)</p>\n<p><strong>Capacity&nbsp;</strong> 40;&nbsp;<strong>Usage&nbsp;</strong> 1/hour</p>\n<p>Sci-shield units protect scientists conducting dangerous fieldwork. The suit excels at deflecting @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.SfkuzH5kxSAmG4nv.JournalEntryPage.n461i9lDXw303SiY#radiation]{Radiation} (granting @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.WP7hddXW4mLXXXOg.JournalEntryPage.8bxhPYw9heXqKHYD#environmental-protections]{Environmental Protection} against radiation as if it were item level 7). A biohacker or mechanic wearing a sci-shield unit treats their class level as two higher than normal for the purpose of determining the range of their @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.lgdDuAM2I3s8PQsD]{Custom Microlab} and @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.AiYxJza4CVXPRjFz]{Remote Hacking} class features.</p>"
